products.name: HAEMMERLIN 5000G GREEN POLY WHEELBARROW
products.description: A great green wheelbarrow for the garden. The 'Poly' has a 90 litre polypropylene tray that is ribbed for added strength. The 32mm tubular one-piece epoxy coated frame is fitted with bi-material grips for added comfort. A 400mm disc wheel is fitted with a solid 2 ply pneumatic tyre.

products.name: FAITHFULL STEEL SHAFTED HATCHET
products.description: All Steel camping hatchet with a bright finish and a comfortable rubber grip. It is supplied with a protective sheath which is slotted so that it can be carried on a belt. Size. 1.1/4lb. Handle length: 11in
